{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 676531, "nreplies": 12, "sticky": 0, "user": "48495", "body": "I can't wait til we get to fight [url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Voltron]Voltron[/url]!  Too bad they couldn't make the first 3 vehicles robot lions!\n\n\nBTW...  I thought [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iC_Z-ebp9Es]Voltron [/url]was supposed to be loved by good and feared by evil.  And where are the 5 space explorers controlling him?   This just doesn't add up.    Did he activate the interlock?  Are the Dyna-therms connected? Are Infracells up?  Most importantly the mega-thrusters better be go!  I really hope there is some audio going along with this fight asking all those [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tZZv5Z2Iz_s]tough questions[/url].  He should have an enrage timer where he \"forms blazing sword\" and just goes nuts on the robeast...  duh i mean raid.  \n\n\nOh and just one more thing, can he please get a <Defender of the Universe> subtag under his name.   That would be awesome.", "date": "2009-04-14T19:44:18-05:00", "rating": 60, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "You didn't ask the most important tough question of all.  Who gets to say, \" . . . and I'll form the head!\"?", "creationdate": "2009-04-15T07:22:41-05:00", "id": 91311, "rating": 45, "commentid": 676531, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "TMWNN", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Useful macro for handling the cores:  [code]#showtooltip item:46029 /use Magnetic Core[/code]", "creationdate": "2009-04-20T21:32:07-05:00", "id": 92745, "rating": 30, "commentid": 676531, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "suicidalkatt", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Bask in its glorious... erm... glory  The coolest quote EVE