{"commentv2": 1, "number": 10, "id": 689727, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "flakmeister", "body": "As a side note, Mimiron is an obvious allusion to  Mimir the Wise, from Norse mythology. \r\nBeing the guardian of a well of wisdom situated at one of the roots of the world tree, Yggdrasil, he would drink deep from it and be granted great knowledge. Odin/Wodan, the All-Father, pulled out one of his eyes from its socket and threw it in the well as payment for being allowed to drink from the waters.\r\n\r\nThe Keepers of Ulduar all having names referencing Norse mythology and said mythology's lack of a real god of wisdom, Mimir was the obvious choice.", "date": "2009-04-22T18:26:55-05:00", "rating": 28, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Also, in the Horde quests (possibly Alliance too, but I've only done Horde) in Storm Peaks, there are many references to the Keeper Mimir - whether this is simply a continuity error by Blizzard and it refers to Mimiron or it is another Keeper entirely we don't know. Either way, it is undeniably a reference to Mimir the Wise.", "creationdate": "2009-10-25T09:35:05-05:00", "id": 429284, "rating": 0, "commentid": 689727, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Xicon", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Hmm. Yeah, I'd personally use V\u00e4inam\u00f6inen for the reference, but that might mess with the theme,", "creationdate": "2009-12-05T10:53:43-06:00", "id": 433262, "rating": 0, "commentid": 689727, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "493096", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "That was an unbearably pretentious comment to make.", "creationdate": "2009-12-07T07:42:01-06:00", "id": 433431, "rating": 3, "commentid": 689727, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Asmodoues", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
