{"commentv2": 1, "number": 43, "id": 772348, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "272760", "body": "In Hard Mode Mimiron helps extinguish the fires:\r\nPhase 1 and 4: The Leviathan MK II casts [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=64570]Flame Suppressant[/url] around the time he casts the 2nd and 4th Shock Blasts.  They cannot occur at the same time, but either one can be cast first.\r\n\r\nPhase 2: the VX-001 will cast out a Frost Bomb into a patch of fire, after a few seconds it explodes dealing [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=64626]9425-10575 damage on Normal[/url] ([url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=65333]47125-52875 Heroic[/url]) in a 30 yard radius and knocking you back.  It also extinguishes the fires in the area. \r\nHe also uses a weaker [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=65192]Flame Suppressant[/url] in this phase, which clears out the fires in melee range.  It is cast often, but never during the Spinning Up/Pewx2 Barrage casts.\r\n\r\nPhase 3: As mentioned, Summons the Emergency Fire Bots.  On Normal Mode these do not Silence you, and on Heroic the Silence seems to only affect melee range.", "date": "2009-07-09T01:07:13-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
