{"commentv2": 1, "number": 61, "id": 1366533, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "667361", "body": "Now doesn't this boss remind you of Dexter from Dexter's Laboratory?\r\nHere are [b]4[/b] reasons why I said so:\r\n\r\n[b]1:[/b] He is a small boy size as a gnome which this model is a nice selection\r\n\r\n[b]2:[/b] In the bosses room, There's a big red button that even says \"DON'T PUSH THIS BUTTON!\"\r\nwhich Dexter's sister, Dee Dee always pushes buttons that cause self-destruct.\r\n\r\n[b]3:[/b] He always build advance technologys which this boss does.\r\n\r\n[b]4:[/b] After you push the big red button, There's a female voice telling the time of self-destruct which is like Dexter's Computer voice.\r\n\r\nSo ye, my point is that this boss must be the reference of Dexter :)", "date": "2011-03-14T07:49:25-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Nah. Invader Zim.", "creationdate": "2014-11-04T00:53:14-06:00", "id": 785640, "rating": -2, "commentid": 1366533, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "KeybladeBandit", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 62, "id": 1563907, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "TheCheat54", "body": "The article for this boss is incorrect regarding Rocket Strikes during Phase 4. It claims that the Leviathan MK II is stunned while Rocket Strikes are being fired, but this only happens while the VX-001 is casting Spinning Up (which, strangely, isn't mentioned in the article).", "date": "2011-11-05T16:58:08-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 63, "id": 1625390, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "947548", "body": "Solo'd easily as a blood DK in 382 ilvl dps gear.\r\n\r\nUse smart use of your cooldowns in phase 1 and 4 and the fight is cake. In phase 4, I just heart struck the middle boss (voltron) and the cleave would damage all the others, including the head. The bottom two had to rebuild themselves a couple time before the head was ready to be taken out, but just power through it and it will ready to kill with the other two, for a third time.", "date": "2012-02-12T11:52:40-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 16384, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
