{"commentv2": 1, "number": 73, "id": 1961176, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Nocked", "body": "Okay here's the trick for Fury warriors. You may need to respec to the talents below. Drag him around the room avoiding Rocket Strike. Take the two bottom parts down to close to death, then focus on the head with Storm Bolt, Dragon Roar, and Heroic Throw every time the cooldowns are up. Once the head is down, finish the other two. This was the only way I could do it.", "date": "2014-04-25T20:15:09-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "As of 6.0.2. stormbolt and dragon roar are on the same talent line. So you have to choose", "creationdate": "2014-10-26T14:32:39-05:00", "id": 782493, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1961176, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Papa63", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 74, "id": 1985832, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "ucplayer", "body": "As a Rogue, use Shuriken Toss to kill the head.", "date": "2014-07-28T18:10:43-05:00", "rating": 8, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "This needs to be easier to find. Had a lot of issues until I turned on Blade Flurry and just spammed Shiruken into the head until about 5% then melted the lower 2.", "creationdate": "2016-01-09T02:15:48-06:00", "id": 923799, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1985832, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Tuckletuts", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
