{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 2409424, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "isendims", "body": "I was flying over Terrace of the Makers in Storm Peaks and a dialog window popped up (the new style dialog in legion) with voice acting stating:\n\n[quote]Indeed, Bronzebeared. Now hold on! I'm taking you in.[/quote]\n\nIt was in a friendly voice as if they were working together on something. I sat there for a moment and it did it again. Seems it keeps saying it about every 1-3 minutes(varies).", "date": "2016-09-20T17:20:57-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Can confirm this, just got it from flying over the are right before Temple of Wisdom, uploading a screenshot asap", "creationdate": "2016-09-22T14:23:10-05:00", "id": 983808, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2409424, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Eonarion", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2016-09-20T17:21:53-05:00", 1, "isendims"]}
