{"commentv2": 1, "number": 5, "id": 2434633, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "SilverRaven64", "body": "With the release of patch 7.1, the Image of Mimiron now offers to return Hati back to the old look;\n\n\"Mimiron, I miss Hati's old look, can you change it back?\"\n\nI've been too scared to use the [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=138393]Essence Swapper[/url], so I have not changed Hati's appearance. Can anyone confirm that this new option works?", "date": "2016-10-25T20:39:21-05:00", "rating": 8, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Just tried it yes he does revert Hati Back to His Original Form", "creationdate": "2016-10-27T13:41:18-05:00", "id": 1001827, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2434633, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "HybridCarnage", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I'm undecided between his original lighter blue form and his dark blackish look after you finish the order campaign. If I revert to the original using this, can I ever get the dark look back?", "creationdate": "2016-11-06T04:31:24-06:00", "id": 1005874, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2434633, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "CallistaZM", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I could be wrong, but I was under the impression that Hati's color was based off of the color of your artifact appearance. When I use the green color from Titanstrike, remove the weapon and then put it back on Hati turns light blue. When I change to the blue for Eaglewatch, remove the weapon and then equip it again then Hati turns black.", "creationdate": "2016-11-10T02:10:29-06:00", "id": 1007249, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2434633, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "SilverRaven64", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2016-10-25T20:48:59-05:00", 4, "SilverRaven64"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 6, "id": 2440430, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "zorozax", "body": "If you are looking for [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=110424]Image of Mimiron[/url] to start the quest for your [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=138393]Essence Swapper[/url]; you can find him inside the Lodge on the small Titan projector pedestal just left of your Grand Challenger's Bounty a.k.a: Mythic + Reward Chest.", "date": "2016-11-05T02:34:34-05:00", "rating": 11, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Thank you! I scooted all over the place IN FRONT of the map and found nothing. Most say it is to the right of it and your description saved my sanity! \ud83d\ude02", "creationdate": "2017-03-01T13:48:24-06:00", "id": 1035193, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2440430, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "stormsmyst", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2016-11-05T03:22:35-05:00", 1, "zorozax"]}
