{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 709551, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Norrec", "body": "This is the version of Mimiron that shows up during the fight against [url=/?npc=33288]Yogg-Saron[/url], for the boss version, please go to  [url=/?npc=33350]this page[/url]. He use the following abilities during the fight :\n\n[ul]\n[li][spell=62671], an aura increasing all damage done by 10% and movement speed by 20%.[/li]\n[li][spell=65210], this spell is periodically casted and reduce the attack and cast speed of Yogg'saron [url=/?npcs&filter=na=tentacle;cr=6;crs=4273;crv=0]tentacles[/url].[/li] \n[/ul]", "date": "2009-05-08T10:27:14-05:00", "rating": 17, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-05-08T12:03:37-05:00", 1, "Norrec"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 711071, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "237317", "body": "Is he a [url=http://www.wowwiki.com/Titan]Titan[/url]?", "date": "2009-05-09T19:52:09-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "He's a mechagnome. They were built by the Titan's. Some of the mechagnomes and earthen were cursed with flesh by Yogg-saron and that's a brief story on the origin of the Gnomes and Dwarves.", "creationdate": "2009-05-20T10:09:56-05:00", "id": 99072, "rating": 5, "commentid": 711071, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Idocreating", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Mechagnomes weren't built by the titans. Mirmiron was built by the titans. And he created mechagnomes because he felt lonely. Some mechagnomes were affected by the \"curse of the flesh\" and became gnomes.  So thanks Mirmiron!", "creationdate": "2009-06-01T07:42:30-05:00", "id": 101322, "rating": 8, "commentid": 711071, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "377386", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "In Borean Tundra there is a quest were you have to kill a head mechagnome who says that he is trying to remove the taint of flesh.", "creationdate": "2009-06-23T17:13:22-05:00", "id": 105582, "rating": 3, "commentid": 711071, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "295697", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Mimiron is in fact a \"Titanic Watcher\", but Blizzard don't put an update for his model :/", "creationdate": "2013-09-01T11:30:09-05:00", "id": 688869, "rating": 0, "commentid": 711071, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "jackblues", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
