{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 2372240, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "PunterHunter", "body": "This NPC will offer the quest [quest=43370] upon reaching 110 as a hunter, the quest rewards the player with [item=138393] which is used to permanently alter Hati's appearance to the currently called pet. After using the item you may talk with the NPC again and he should offer an option to revert the Hati back to his original appearance. [npc=106557] can be found to the right of the scouting map on the holopad beside the weekly mythic dungeon chest in Trueshot Lodge, simply approach it after reaching 110 and he should offer the rather grindy quest. He will only appear while you are in beast mastery spec\ncurrently [npc=107469] is plagued with phasing issues so the fastest way to get the [item=139349] is to farm [npc=99223].", "date": "2016-08-22T17:31:30-05:00", "rating": 16, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "So when and where does he pop up?", "creationdate": "2016-09-06T02:16:02-05:00", "id": 969588, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2372240, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "mshep02", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "@msheph02 - As you walk by a tiny, circular platform on the left side (facing the doorway) of the Trueshot Lodge, to take the portal to Dalaran, the platform begins charging up and the Image of Mimiron appears. Right click to begin interacting with him and he'll give you the quest.", "creationdate": "2016-09-10T11:52:31-05:00", "id": 974114, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2372240, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Violante", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Weird, because my affliction warlock was just taking a taxi from (old) Dalaran to Ulduar, and this popped up for me!", "creationdate": "2018-01-28T18:37:30-06:00", "id": 1096816, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2372240, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "chindok", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2017-08-15T01:47:32-05:00", 6, "PunterHunter"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2382504, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "THRobinson", "body": "Looking for the Time-Lost Proto-Drake, and this is constantly popping up saying \"Indeed, Bronzebeard, now hold on! I'm taking you in\".\r\n\r\nNever had the issue before, now can't shut him up. :S", "date": "2016-09-02T13:48:39-05:00", "rating": 16, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Same thing happens to me. Im not sure why it says that or what its supposed to indicate", "creationdate": "2016-10-12T17:44:42-05:00", "id": 995579, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2382504, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "toxsick", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Came here looking for the same thing, was heading to Ulduar for pet runs and this just came up out of the blue. At first I thought maybe it had something to do with the quest area, but it uses the new NPC dialog box like from Warcraft and you don't actually get quests from him when in Northrend. More glitches as usual.", "creationdate": "2016-11-15T18:07:09-06:00", "id": 1009032, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2382504, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Jeolene", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}